<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_106_r2l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> wir <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l3">wir befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . etlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> notdurft als von des geleyts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l4">
<add><ab facs="#facs_106_r1l1"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu vnd </ab></add> von der <expan>nehſtkünftıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> vaſtenmeſſe . an eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l5"><expan>brıng<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>g<ex>ancʒem</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>leiſſ</ex></expan> VVas <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l6"><expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅr gnade alſo <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> . daʒ Jr Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l7">darinn gütlıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> Jm des <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd auch <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l8">eẅch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet / als etc das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
