<ab>Bischof zu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        notdurft als von des geleyts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den
                                    <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu und</add> von der
                                <expan>nehstkünftig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> vastenmesse an ewr
                                <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade zu
                            <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>g<ex>anczem</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>leiss</ex></expan>, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade also
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir in darinn gütlich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>, im des
                            <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        von ewch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet als etc. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> letare.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Johannsen, grafen zu Wertheim<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lienhart<ex>en</ex></expan>, grafen und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                            Castell<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Schenken, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                                Lympurg<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Pickembach
                        und <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan><lb/><expan>Ha<ex>n</ex>man</expan>
                        Echter, vicztum zu
                                <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan><lb/><expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von Seckendorff von Winspach, <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu der
                        Newenstat an der Eysch <expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
